{"tid":1917292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國代表在WHO會議上寸爆譚德塞","createTime":"2020-03-09T11:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T12:32:38.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7af8de54de71a3e572d3e53ce4ab0556b73c6437","tid":1917292,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1678608719047846/videos/1523599517798703/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1678608719047846%2Fvideos%2F1523599517798703%2F%20&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=ad9efc70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1678608719047846/videos/1523599517798703/ </a>"},{"pid":"5926fd377a9daa7b576b9a82b1a85e870aa3a08f","tid":1917292,"uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"「主席，全球新冠肺炎的旅行禁令\b都沒人在鳥的，例如WHO幹事長譚德塞，他才剛去過北京，現在又來坐在這裡開會，我們大家都有被傳染的危險，尤其是你，主席，你最危險，因為你一直坐在幹事長旁邊！ 我個人倒是很安全，因為過去這幾天幹事長都不跟我握手。<br />\n<br />\n但我們還是要阻止世人產生無謂的驚慌，要重建大家對WHO的信心！<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於此，主席，我建議啦，我們WHO應該馬上到中國開個會，尤其是武漢，現在正是造訪有兩千年歷史的黃鶴樓的最佳時機！去北京也行，可以去長城、紫禁城，現在不但人少空曠、價格也便宜！<br />\n<br />\n主席，我已經徵得我太太的同意，我願意捐出我半年退休金，另外再自掏腰包來籌辦這個WHO在中國的會議，謝謝！」"},{"pid":"87561ad26c54006ee43bcc3e0c6ac421ae039283","tid":1917292,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=490551308304226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D490551308304226&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=f60297ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=490551308304226</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條link有埋支方翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577952d7dc7c195b282a70b69b86a4446ec88d28","tid":1917292,"uid":60773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim